<h2 class="usa-heading" id="colors">Colors</h2>

<p>The Chicago Design system colors are designed to meet WCAG 2.0 AA standards, while drawing from Chicago's rich history and iconography.</p>


<h3 class="usa-heading" id="palette">Palette</h3>


<p>Rather than be exhaustive, this palette is meant to be a minimalist description of chicago's color identity.</p>

